00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:36.892
to come down as a human being to work out the salvation of the people.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:55.892
It is said that He came to India, in Kashmir,

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:01.892
and He met there the King Shalivahana.

