00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:22.892
who was a great devotee of the Mother.

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:28.892
And he asked Him, “What is Your name?” In Sanskrit it’s all written.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:36.892
