00:22:59.000 --> 00:23:01.892
and people accept it because it’s in the Koran.

00:23:02.000 --> 00:23:05.892
Somebody has made fun of Koran and written what's wrong,

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:08.892
and it’s so stupidities, and all that.

00:23:09.000 --> 00:23:12.892
